metadata.name: Morning Mushroom
metadata.description:
This story will show the moment before the start of the war in Ukraine.

How many people were planning their tomorrow, how many people were planning their lives in this country... But one morning changed everything...

The morning, when instead of an alarm clock, people heard rocket explosions...
This moment forever changed the lives of millions of people from Ukraine, and I am one of them.

Material : Oil paint canvas and digital painting.
